originalText.text: Without getting into too many details, I have to thank this man for giving our baby a chance when 4 other doctors and 2 different hospitals said nothing can be done, he took a look at our case and saved our baby. I hugged him 3x and cried thanking him over and over. It's amazing what God can accomplish through people like Dr. Bruce Feinberg. We still have a long road ahead, but he has made the path clearer.

originalText.text: Dr. Bruce was a life saver during my C.Section. He did his best to save me and my child. Looking at how much blood I lost due to placenta previa, i was infused more than 8 times when haemoglobin level dropped to 8 and hematocrit was 18. I'm doing well, and baby is blessed.  We appreciate the team, and I say God BLESS YOU Dr.Bruce. I made the best choice to chose you to do my C. Section. I love NYPH. I and my baby wouldn't have survived without you guys. Long story short.... Long live Dr.Bruce, Long live NYPH. love and trust u guys to death!
